cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on natural language processing tasks, specifically on out-of-vocabulary lexical evaluation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of unsupervised word embedding methods also suggests a possible fit with sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves text classification and prediction tasks, which could fall under sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
